26
00:04:36,952 --> 00:04:38,223
Ils vont revenir.

27
00:04:38,300 --> 00:04:40,303
Qui a eu l'idée ?

28
00:04:40,399 --> 00:04:42,051
Durrell.

29
00:04:42,552 --> 00:04:44,300
T'es malade ?

30
00:04:46,260 --> 00:04:48,033
Non, je me réveille c'est tout.

31
